entries.journal_entry_description: The Alliance needs to secure any remains of the Imperial research in Restuss. You've been tasked with aiding in securing the city by defeating 20 Imperial soldiers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You have been tasked with defeating 20 Imperial soldiers in Restuss.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You've defeated 20 Imperial soldiers and should return to Captain Redding.
